1. Introduction
At SafeHer, your privacy and security are our top priorities. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use the SafeHer mobile application ("App").
2. Information We Collect
We collect the following data to provide SafeHer’s safety features:
•	Personal Information: Name, phone number, and email address for account creation and identification.
•	Location Data: Real-time tracking is enabled only when safety features are turned on and stops upon deactivation.
•	Emergency Contacts: The App accesses but does not store emergency contact details.
•	Device Information: Information such as phone model and operating system for troubleshooting and security enhancements.
3. How We Use Your Data
•	To enable emergency alerts and safety navigation.
•	To capture and send video/audio evidence to emergency contacts or law enforcement.
•	To process subscription payments securely.
•	To improve and maintain app functionality and user experience.
4. Data Protection and Compliance
•	SafeHer uses encryption and secure storage to protect user data.
•	We comply with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and India’s Information Technology Act for data protection.
•	We do not share user data with third parties for advertising or marketing purposes.
5. Data Retention and User Control
•	User data is retained only for as long as necessary to provide services.
•	Location tracking can be disabled at any time.
6. Third-Party Services
•	SafeHer integrates Firebase for secure backend operations, Google Maps for location tracking, and a payment gateway for subscription processing.
•	These services have their own privacy policies, which apply to users when interacting with them.
7. Your Rights
•	Users can access, update, or request deletion of their personal information.
•	Users can opt out of data collection by discontinuing use of the App.
8. Policy Updates
SafeHer reserves the right to update this Privacy Policy as needed. We will notify users of any significant changes.
9. Contact Us
For privacy concerns or questions, please contact us at safehervideo@gmail.com.
By using SafeHer, you acknowledge and accept this Privacy Policy.
